&lt;li&gt;Improve the quality of Vectara’s AI Agents and RAG-as-a-service platform, working on features like multilinguality, self-supervised learning, agentic behavior and hallucination reduction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Publish technical blogs, papers, and patents.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
